info.description:
itk-minimalpathextraction provides a minimal path extraction framework based on Fast Marching arrival functions.
Please refer to:
Mueller, D. "Fast Marching Minimal Path Extraction in ITK", Insight Journal, January-June 2008, https://hdl.handle.net/1926/1332.
